00:19:48.420 --> 00:19:49.920
to like women in high heels?

00:19:49.920 --> 00:19:51.000
Like, yes, click it.

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:52.620
This is sort of like a
kind of a piece that--

00:19:52.620 --> 00:19:53.520
LOGAN URY: Well,
there's that new book

00:19:53.520 --> 00:19:55.650
that came out "Casual
