00:19:55.650 --> 00:19:57.442
Tinder is affecting monogamy.

00:19:57.442 --> 00:19:59.400
And I think it reinforces
a lot of these ideas.

00:19:59.400 --> 00:19:59.700
So it's still--

00:19:59.700 --> 00:20:01.140
MOIRA WEIGEL: Oh, what
does that book say?

00:20:01.140 --> 00:20:02.070
LOGAN URY: I
haven't read it yet.

00:20:02.070 --> 00:20:03.420
I just read an article about it.

00:20:03.420 --> 00:20:07.410
But it was basically saying that
