00:20:10.020 --> 00:20:11.400
and an ability to reproduce.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:14.605
But now with Tinder, men
have this easy access to sex

00:20:14.605 --> 00:20:15.230
when they want.

00:20:15.230 --> 00:20:17.640
So there's this bifurcation
between the place

00:20:17.640 --> 00:20:20.610
I go for sex and the place I go
for marriage, which is leading

00:20:20.610 --> 00:20:22.055
fewer people to want marriage.

00:20:22.055 --> 00:20:23.430
MOIRA WEIGEL: It's
really amazing

00:20:23.430 --> 00:20:26.220
how many respectable academics
and scholars in 2017,

00:20:26.220 --> 00:20:29.950
it's never occurred to them
