00:22:52.780 --> 00:22:56.200
and it's popularized
for much beyond,

00:22:56.200 --> 00:22:58.990
much longer than it's existed in
its institutionalized academic

00:22:58.990 --> 00:22:59.530
form.

00:22:59.530 --> 00:23:01.030
LOGAN URY: I love how
