among people than--

00:23:56.240 --> 00:23:58.620
in this one class than
across the classes.

00:23:58.620 --> 00:24:01.640
And so I think that, again, it's
reassuring to certain people

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:04.460
to believe that what
is natural is good

00:24:04.460 --> 00:24:07.110
and that nature sanctions a
certain kind of social order.

00:24:07.110 --> 00:24:09.980
