usually not a very useful

00:24:09.980 --> 00:24:12.740
and certainly not a
very progressive way

00:24:12.740 --> 00:24:14.820
to think about our
relations as humans.

00:24:14.820 --> 00:24:16.160
LOGAN URY: So I just want to
